2
00:00:02,910 --> 00:00:05,940
(Episode 6)

3
00:00:08,310 --> 00:00:10,279
What took you so long?

4
00:00:10,720 --> 00:00:12,220
Oh, I was...

5
00:00:12,779 --> 00:00:14,990
I prayed for the dead one.

6
00:00:16,089 --> 00:00:17,489
You guys do that too?

7
00:00:19,089 --> 00:00:22,059
Yes. It's because
my hobby is praying.

8
00:00:22,329 --> 00:00:24,699
Then why did you take this
corpse out again?

9
00:00:25,760 --> 00:00:26,899
It's a different one.

10
00:00:27,899 --> 00:00:29,399
This one needs to go
to a different city.

11
00:00:30,170 --> 00:00:31,239
Have a good night.

12
00:00:32,369 --> 00:00:34,310
(Chapel of Rest)

13
00:00:36,570 --> 00:00:38,280
What kind of a corpse
is wearing shoes?

14
00:00:39,979 --> 00:00:41,780
I'm going to a convenience store.
Do you need anything?

15
00:00:42,079 --> 00:00:43,079
I'll go.

16
00:00:43,079 --> 00:00:44,950
I want to get some fresh air.
What do you want?

17
00:00:45,649 --> 00:00:47,289
I want a fish cake bar and a Coke.

18
00:00:47,350 --> 00:00:48,990
Okay, I'll get a hot dog for you.

19
00:00:49,320 --> 00:00:51,520
Dae Young, I said one fish cake bar
and a Coke.

20
00:01:01,770 --> 00:01:03,329
I knew something was up.

21
00:01:04,400 --> 00:01:06,269
Why is that priest so persistent?

22
00:01:07,170 --> 00:01:08,209
What should I do?

23
00:01:08,810 --> 00:01:10,439
What else can I do?
I have to report.

24
00:01:12,439 --> 00:01:14,280
You're not going to use
your taser, right?

25
00:01:14,349 --> 00:01:16,150
Yes, because I have
only one cartridge left.

26
00:01:21,290 --> 00:01:22,989
If you were to speak to yourself,
you should've been quiet.

27
00:01:24,420 --> 00:01:25,989
Your voice echoed in the hallway.

28
00:01:25,989 --> 00:01:28,260
Father, you've done
something really bad.

29
00:01:29,930 --> 00:01:31,200
Who's the guy you came with?

30
00:01:31,430 --> 00:01:32,599
He's the examiner of NISI.

31
00:01:32,599 --> 00:01:34,000
NISI?

32
00:01:34,430 --> 00:01:35,969
Then you've done
illegal autopsy as well?

33
00:01:36,200 --> 00:01:38,099
I didn't go that far. I just checked
the corpse's outer parts.

34
00:01:38,569 --> 00:01:39,769
Still, that's not right.

35
00:01:40,909 --> 00:01:42,769
Then report it. Report it,
and let's go to hell together.

36
00:01:44,209 --> 00:01:45,609
I'm a priest,

37
00:01:46,109 --> 00:01:47,609
so it's nothing to take you
to hell with me.

38
00:01:50,819 --> 00:01:52,680
You don't know what kind
of a place hell is, do you?

39
00:01:55,189 --> 00:01:56,319
The fiery hell?

40
00:01:57,019 --> 00:01:58,260
It's not where...

41
00:01:59,290 --> 00:02:00,290
