63
00:03:35,919 --> 00:03:39,520
It's living the same life
you're living infinitely.

64
00:03:39,689 --> 00:03:40,729
Darn it!

65
00:03:41,490 --> 00:03:43,360
In layman's terms,

66
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:47,629
