over and over...

67
00:03:47,629 --> 00:03:49,270
I got it! Get lost already!

68
00:03:50,669 --> 00:03:51,699
Go!

69
00:03:51,939 --> 00:03:54,340
I tried to explain it
as easy as I could.

70
00:03:55,409 --> 00:03:57,180
- Go!
- Okay, I'm going.

71
00:03:57,280 --> 00:03:59,439
- Go!
- Why are you yelling at me?

72
00:04:00,039 --> 00:04:01,080
Go!

73
00:04:39,620 --> 00:04:41,019
There are kids in there!

74
00:04:41,019 --> 00:04:43,990
There are no kids in there!
I checked already!

75
00:04:44,060 --> 00:04:45,689
Do you want to die?
Throw the grenade!

76
00:04:46,060 --> 00:04:47,430
I said, throw it!

77
00:05:31,199 --> 00:05:33,040
(Intelligence makes
a strong nation.)

78
00:05:56,959 --> 00:05:59,430
All records of Agent Kim Hae Il
of National Intelligence Service...

79
00:05:59,759 --> 00:06:00,769
will be erased.

80
00:06:00,769 --> 00:06:01,970
(NIS works for national security and
to promote the national interest.)

81
00:06:01,970 --> 00:06:04,370
You'll become a normal man
who's lived a normal life.

82
00:06:05,540 --> 00:06:06,839
That's all the help I can give.

83
00:06:56,089 --> 00:06:57,120
Sit down.

84
00:07:05,060 --> 00:07:06,259
Are you here to pray?

85
00:07:06,829 --> 00:07:07,870
No.

86
00:07:08,529 --> 00:07:12,170
I came because I missed Father Lee.

87
00:07:15,709 --> 00:07:16,870
Was he good to you?

88
00:07:18,810 --> 00:07:19,910
He was...

89
00:07:21,110 --> 00:07:24,019
like an angel to me.

90
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:29,050
I came to this neighborhood
with only five dollars on me.

91
00:07:29,819 --> 00:07:32,459
I had no food to eat
or a place to stay.

92
00:07:35,259 --> 00:07:39,000
Father Lee fed me
and gave me a place to stay.

93
00:07:40,730 --> 00:07:43,699
He even helped me get a... A jab?

94
00:07:44,040 --> 00:07:45,100
A job.

95
00:07:45,240 --> 00:07:47,769
Yes, he helped me get a job.

96
00:07:48,839 --> 00:07:51,709
I see. Which country are you from?

97
00:07:52,279 --> 00:07:53,850
I'm from Thailand.

98
00:07:54,180 --> 00:07:55,579
Why did you come here?

99
00:07:55,910 --> 00:07:58,319
I have to make a lot of money.

100
